org.mixare.plugin.remoteobjects

Class RemoteMarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mixare.plugin.remoteobjects.RemoteMarker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Marker>, Marker

    public class RemoteMarker
extends java.lang.Object
implements Marker
    The remote marker sends request to the (remote)plugin that it is connected to through IMarkerService. the remote marker is treated like a normal marker in the core. And it overrides the marker interface.
    Author:
    A. Egal
